#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.110"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.110:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.110:0.2"
msgid "11. Valāhakavagga"
msgstr "11. Clouds"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: āsivisasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.110:0.3"
msgid "110. Āsīvisasutta"
msgstr "110. Vipers"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.111"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: āsīvisā → āsivisā (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an4.110:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, āsīvisā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four kinds of viper."

msgctxt "an4.110:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.110:1.3"
msgid ""
"Āgataviso na ghoraviso, ghoraviso na āgataviso, āgataviso ca ghoraviso ca, "
"nevāgataviso na ghoraviso—"
msgstr ""
"~One whose venom is fast-acting but not lethal, ~one whose venom is lethal "
"but not fast-acting, ~one whose venom is both fast-acting and lethal, and ~"
"one whose venom is neither fast-acting nor lethal."

msgctxt "an4.110:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro āsīvisā."
msgstr "These are the four kinds of viper."

msgctxt "an4.110:1.5"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cattāro āsīvisūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā "
"lokasmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, these four people similar to vipers are found in the world."

msgctxt "an4.110:1.6"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.110:1.7"
msgid ""
"Āgataviso na ghoraviso, ghoraviso na āgataviso, āgataviso ca ghoraviso ca, "
"nevāgataviso na ghoraviso."
msgstr ""
"~One whose venom is fast-acting but not lethal, ~one whose venom is lethal "
"but not fast-acting, ~one whose venom is both fast-acting and lethal, and ~"
"one whose venom is neither fast-acting nor lethal."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.110:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo āgataviso hoti, na ghoraviso?"
msgstr "And how is a person’s venom fast-acting but not lethal?"

msgctxt "an4.110:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo abhiṇhaṃ kujjhati."
msgstr "It’s when a person is often angry,"

#. VAR: kodho → kopo (mr)
msgctxt "an4.110:2.3"
msgid "So ca khvassa kodho na dīgharattaṃ anuseti."
msgstr "but their anger doesn’t linger long."

msgctxt "an4.110:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo āgataviso hoti, na ghoraviso."
msgstr "That’s how a person’s venom is fast-acting but not lethal."

msgctxt "an4.110:2.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, āsīviso āgataviso, na ghoraviso;"
msgstr "That person is like a viper whose venom is fast-acting but not lethal."

msgctxt "an4.110:2.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.110:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo ghoraviso hoti, na āgataviso?"
msgstr "And how is a person’s venom lethal but not fast-acting?"

msgctxt "an4.110:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo na heva kho abhiṇhaṃ kujjhati."
msgstr "It’s when a person is not often angry,"

msgctxt "an4.110:3.3"
msgid "So ca khvassa kodho dīgharattaṃ anuseti."
msgstr "but their anger lingers for a long time."

msgctxt "an4.110:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo ghoraviso hoti, na āgataviso."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.110:3.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, āsīviso ghoraviso, na āgataviso;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.110:3.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.110:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo āgataviso ca hoti ghoraviso ca?"
msgstr "And how is a person’s venom both fast-acting and lethal?"

msgctxt "an4.110:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo abhiṇhaṃ kujjhati."
msgstr "It’s when a person is often angry,"

msgctxt "an4.110:4.3"
msgid "So ca khvassa kodho dīgharattaṃ anuseti."
msgstr "and their anger lingers for a long time."

msgctxt "an4.110:4.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo āgataviso ca hoti ghoraviso ca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.110:4.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, āsīviso āgataviso ca ghoraviso ca;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.110:4.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.110:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo nevāgataviso hoti na ghoraviso?"
msgstr "And how is a person’s venom neither fast-acting nor lethal?"

msgctxt "an4.110:5.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo na heva kho abhiṇhaṃ kujjhati."
msgstr "It’s when a person is not often angry,"

msgctxt "an4.110:5.3"
msgid "So ca khvassa kodho na dīgharattaṃ anuseti."
msgstr "and their anger doesn’t linger long."

msgctxt "an4.110:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo nevāgataviso hoti, na ghoraviso."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.110:5.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, āsīviso nevāgataviso na ghoraviso;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.110:5.6"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.110:5.7"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro āsīvisūpamā puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā "
"lokasmin”ti."
msgstr "These four people similar to vipers are found in the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.110:5.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.110:5.9"
msgid "Valāhakavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.110:6.1"
msgid "Dve valāhā kumbha udaka,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.110:6.2"
msgid "rahadā dve honti ambāni;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.110:6.3"
msgid "Mūsikā balībaddā rukkhā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.110:6.4"
msgid "āsīvisena te dasāti."
msgstr ""
